    <div class="body">
        <p>Hello,
i am using Actionscript3 and Zend_Amf to retrieve Data from a Database, which works quite fine in the beginning, but after about  230 NetConnections (sometimes also far earlier) i get this Error:</p>

<p>Error opening URL '<a href="/index.php">http://www.{URL}/index.php</a>'
